WEBVTT

00:00:10.600 --> 00:00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

00:01:06.540 --> 00:01:07.220
[The Eternal Fragrance]

00:01:07.220 --> 00:01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

00:01:12.020 --> 00:01:15.140
[Episode 30]

00:01:15.720 --> 00:01:16.340
Stop.

00:01:17.360 --> 00:01:17.940
Go back.

00:01:18.080 --> 00:01:20.170
I've been preparing for this battle for five hundred years!

00:01:20.640 --> 00:01:21.650
I can't let it all fall apart now!

00:01:24.720 --> 00:01:25.940
You dare defy me?

00:01:53.160 --> 00:01:53.890
Investigate it.

00:02:23.520 --> 00:02:24.130
With this,

00:02:24.520 --> 00:02:26.180
Can we root out all evil cultivators

00:02:26.200 --> 00:02:26.810
In the city?

00:02:27.640 --> 00:02:29.250
Mr. Mo's artifact never fails.

00:02:31.110 --> 00:02:31.850
Ready?

00:02:47.360 --> 00:02:47.900
Tongzhou.

00:04:10.150 --> 00:04:10.620
Let me help you.

00:04:22.000 --> 00:04:22.620
Feeling much better.

00:04:22.640 --> 00:04:23.300
What's going on?

00:04:37.390 --> 00:04:38.010
Lifei?

00:04:38.790 --> 00:04:40.210
The Divine Tree's power can purify demonic energy.

00:04:55.230 --> 00:04:55.740
My Lord.

00:04:57.270 --> 00:04:57.740
Hurry over!

00:04:58.760 --> 00:04:59.210
How is it?

00:05:29.150 --> 00:05:30.540
I killed Mr. Shen.

00:05:31.080 --> 00:05:32.420
Once I wipe you insignificant pests out,

00:05:32.760 --> 00:05:33.810
Duanming City will be mine.

00:05:34.560 --> 00:05:35.420
Demon, don't you dare!

00:05:35.910 --> 00:05:36.300
Fall into formation!!

00:06:10.760 --> 00:06:11.250
Xiuyuan,

00:06:11.880 --> 00:06:12.620
Leave Qiongqi here.

00:06:13.350 --> 00:06:14.420
I'm sorry, Mr. Mo.

00:06:15.320 --> 00:06:16.420
I have to take him away.

00:06:17.150 --> 00:06:17.860
Lei Xiuyuan,

00:06:18.200 --> 00:06:19.180
He killed my father.

00:06:30.680 --> 00:06:31.370
Hand over Qiongqi!

00:06:37.830 --> 00:06:38.450
Lei Xiuyuan,

00:06:38.960 --> 00:06:39.890
Hand over Qiongqi,

00:06:40.440 --> 00:06:41.100
And I'll spare you.

00:06:44.030 --> 00:06:44.810
I leave when I please.

00:06:45.520 --> 00:06:46.660
None of you may stop me.

00:07:14.030 --> 00:07:14.540
Tongzhou,

00:07:14.880 --> 00:07:15.330
You're hurt.

00:07:15.350 --> 00:07:15.940
Stop fighting.

00:07:45.440 --> 00:07:46.060
Miss Jiang,

00:07:46.960 --> 00:07:47.860
His Highness has rested.

00:07:50.030 --> 00:07:51.300
Is he furious?

00:07:51.680 --> 00:07:52.770
The Demon Lord wounded him,

00:07:53.080 --> 00:07:54.130
Yet you sided with that demon.

00:07:54.520 --> 00:07:55.540
How can he bear this,

00:07:55.560 --> 00:07:57.300
Especially since he's always guarded you?

00:07:58.120 --> 00:07:58.890
Lifei,

00:07:59.270 --> 00:08:00.770
You know full well that he loves you.

00:08:01.390 --> 00:08:02.740
Why do you keep hurting him?

00:08:04.470 --> 00:08:05.210
It's not like that.

00:08:08.120 --> 00:08:09.180
Please leave.

00:08:09.880 --> 00:08:10.500
His Highness said

00:08:11.030 --> 00:08:11.940
He won't see anyone.

00:09:09.280 --> 00:09:11.060
Once inner demons arise,

00:09:11.590 --> 00:09:13.450
How can one calm oneself?

00:09:15.080 --> 00:09:16.570
So what of inner demons?

00:09:18.040 --> 00:09:19.900
Once I reach the fifth level of Xuanhua Sacred Fire

00:09:20.680 --> 00:09:21.810
And become immortal,

00:09:22.710 --> 00:09:23.300
The Divine Tree,

00:09:24.990 --> 00:09:25.850
Lifei,

00:09:27.680 --> 00:09:29.380
Will never leave my side.

00:09:38.470 --> 00:09:40.540
Qiongqi killed our master?

00:09:41.710 --> 00:09:42.690
He admitted it himself.

00:09:43.830 --> 00:09:45.210
Your name is clear.

00:09:45.510 --> 00:09:46.450
The night our master was killed,

00:09:47.080 --> 00:09:48.570
I fought Qiongqi on Yingcui Island.

00:09:49.280 --> 00:09:50.540
He couldn't have killed our master.

00:09:52.440 --> 00:09:54.490
You mean someone else did?

00:09:58.080 --> 00:09:59.140
This person killed our master

00:09:59.750 --> 00:10:00.780
And can command demon beasts.

00:10:01.320 --> 00:10:02.260
If he's still in the city,

00:10:02.710 --> 00:10:03.450
He'll be a grave peril.

00:10:06.990 --> 00:10:08.020
Where is Qiongqi now?

00:10:09.280 --> 00:10:10.850
Xiuyuan took it away.

00:10:11.710 --> 00:10:12.810
Word goes

00:10:13.470 --> 00:10:14.900
That Lifei let them escape.

00:10:19.080 --> 00:10:19.730
Jiang Lifei,

00:10:20.280 --> 00:10:21.420
You colluded with the demon clan

00:10:21.440 --> 00:10:22.570
And let the Demon Lord go on purpose.

00:10:22.870 --> 00:10:24.450
Everyone there saw it.

00:10:24.920 --> 00:10:27.060
Now, how will you deny it?

00:10:27.680 --> 00:10:28.660
I won't deny anything.

00:10:28.990 --> 00:10:29.730
You admit it?

00:10:32.590 --> 00:10:34.140
Lei Xiuyuan came here to help.

00:10:34.830 --> 00:10:35.970
Thanks to him, we've rooted out

00:10:35.990 --> 00:10:37.330
All disciples practicing the demonic arts

00:10:37.350 --> 00:10:38.090
Within the city.

00:10:38.470 --> 00:10:39.300
Why would he do that?

00:10:40.230 --> 00:10:41.660
Isn't Qiongqi his subordinate?

00:10:42.510 --> 00:10:43.810
I don't know why, either.

00:10:44.440 --> 00:10:46.180
But as Elder Guangwei's former disciple,

00:10:47.280 --> 00:10:49.730
Perhaps he still holds affection for the sect.

00:10:50.280 --> 00:10:52.260
I think he still holds feelings for you.

00:10:52.590 --> 00:10:53.140
Makes sense.

00:10:53.440 --> 00:10:54.970
You both came from overseas

00:10:55.200 --> 00:10:56.540
And studied in the same academy.

00:10:56.870 --> 00:10:58.610
What a deep bond you share.

00:11:00.080 --> 00:11:01.540
As my cultivation partner,

00:11:01.960 --> 00:11:03.420
Lifei has no affection for another.

00:11:06.870 --> 00:11:07.450
Tongzhou.

00:11:08.160 --> 00:11:08.810
Hush.

00:11:11.440 --> 00:11:12.330
Your Highness,

00:11:12.560 --> 00:11:13.900
We all understand

00:11:13.920 --> 00:11:15.060
You defend Jiang Lifei

00:11:15.400 --> 00:11:16.570
Out of old friendship.

00:11:16.590 --> 00:11:17.780
But don't go blabbing

00:11:18.080 --> 00:11:19.090
About certain connections.

00:11:21.470 --> 00:11:23.140
She and I met when we were young

00:11:23.320 --> 00:11:24.420
And have long loved each other.

00:11:25.320 --> 00:11:27.380
Before Elder Xuanshan died,

00:11:27.510 --> 00:11:29.020
We agreed to be cultivation partners.

00:11:35.960 --> 00:11:38.020
But back then, the Xingzheng Hall fell into disaster,

00:11:38.230 --> 00:11:39.020
And the Yue State was attacked,

00:11:39.320 --> 00:11:40.450
So we never announced it to the world.

00:11:40.920 --> 00:11:44.180
Yet she clearly sides with Lei Xiuyuan.

00:11:44.800 --> 00:11:45.380
Word has it

00:11:45.590 --> 00:11:46.660
She even stopped you.

00:11:46.680 --> 00:11:47.940
That was my own order.

00:11:52.200 --> 00:11:54.420
Lei Xiuyuan and I were once fellow disciples.

00:11:54.800 --> 00:11:56.210
He helped me slay Zong Quan,

00:11:56.560 --> 00:11:57.690
And I owe him a favor.

00:11:58.440 --> 00:11:59.450
This debt is mine to repay.

00:12:00.400 --> 00:12:01.260
After today,

00:12:02.200 --> 00:12:03.380
We shall owe each other nothing.

00:12:03.590 --> 00:12:05.420
Did you tell her to stand up

00:12:05.560 --> 00:12:07.060
For that demon earlier?

00:12:09.080 --> 00:12:10.380
I believe what she said.

00:12:11.040 --> 00:12:13.090
Lei Xiuyuan once studied at the Chufeng Academy.

00:12:13.710 --> 00:12:15.330
I truly think he means to help us.

00:12:16.110 --> 00:12:17.570
If he hadn't retrieved the Spirit-Devouring demonic energy,

00:12:17.990 --> 00:12:19.420
I could never have forged that artifact.

00:12:19.680 --> 00:12:20.690
Though he's the Demon Lord,

00:12:21.350 --> 00:12:22.490
He's still human at heart.

00:12:29.200 --> 00:12:29.690
Everyone,

00:12:30.440 --> 00:12:32.660
Even if Lei Xiuyuan bears us no ill will,

00:12:32.680 --> 00:12:34.330
Can the blood feud between us

00:12:34.350 --> 00:12:35.330
And the demon clan vanish?

00:12:35.710 --> 00:12:36.490
Were the Wuyue Court,

00:12:36.510 --> 00:12:37.210
Mr. Shen,

00:12:37.230 --> 00:12:38.610
And all the disciples from the East Sea

00:12:38.630 --> 00:12:39.730
Meant to die in vain?

00:12:46.920 --> 00:12:48.540
Good and evil sects share irreconcilable hatred.

00:12:49.350 --> 00:12:50.380
He threw Duanming City into chaos,

00:12:50.400 --> 00:12:51.300
His crime unforgivable.

00:12:51.750 --> 00:12:53.810
The Sea Sects will never reconcile with the demon clan.

00:13:33.960 --> 00:13:37.650
♪The warmth within my arms♪

00:13:38.030 --> 00:13:41.070
♪I can no longer hold on to♪

00:13:41.370 --> 00:13:44.770
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

00:13:45.130 --> 00:13:48.400
♪Keep you warm until sunrise?♪

00:13:48.770 --> 00:13:51.970
♪My heartbeat freezes♪

00:13:52.290 --> 00:13:55.490
♪I can no longer tell you♪

00:13:55.890 --> 00:13:57.590
♪Looking you in the eyes, I cannot♪

00:13:57.590 --> 00:13:58.260
You're waiting for me?

00:13:59.350 --> 00:14:00.490
Why rescue Qiongqi?

00:14:01.630 --> 00:14:02.570
He killed Mr. Shen

00:14:02.800 --> 00:14:03.570
And should pay with his life.

00:14:04.680 --> 00:14:06.060
Someone else killed Mr. Shen.

00:14:06.710 --> 00:14:07.450
If I hadn't taken him away,

00:14:07.830 --> 00:14:08.810
More people would have died.

00:14:09.470 --> 00:14:10.330
You stopped Tongzhou

00:14:10.630 --> 00:14:12.180
To stop pointless bloodshed, didn't you?

00:14:12.180 --> 00:14:15.870
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

00:14:15.870 --> 00:14:17.380
Yet some hatreds in this world

00:14:18.350 --> 00:14:19.490
Can never be erased.

00:14:19.490 --> 00:14:21.050
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

00:14:21.330 --> 00:14:24.290
♪But we thought nothing of it♪

00:14:24.470 --> 00:14:25.490
Leave with your clansmen.

00:14:25.490 --> 00:14:27.040
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

00:14:27.040 --> 00:14:27.610
If you stay,

00:14:29.080 --> 00:14:30.660
We'll fight till death.

00:14:31.850 --> 00:14:33.530
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

00:14:34.440 --> 00:14:35.260
Fight till death?

00:14:35.260 --> 00:14:37.080
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

00:14:37.080 --> 00:14:37.810
I'd like to see

00:14:39.230 --> 00:14:40.570
If there's another way out.

00:14:41.350 --> 00:14:42.450
No matter what you do,

00:14:42.960 --> 00:14:44.020
Demons are still demons.

00:14:44.630 --> 00:14:46.260
The immortal sects of the Central Plains will never accept you.

00:14:47.400 --> 00:14:48.730
Go back to your islands,

00:14:48.750 --> 00:14:49.940
And never return.

00:14:50.450 --> 00:14:53.290
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

00:14:54.680 --> 00:14:55.660
We will go back to our homeland,

00:14:57.630 --> 00:14:58.810
But not with hatred in our hearts.

00:15:01.590 --> 00:15:02.690
Master Qingcheng spent

00:15:03.230 --> 00:15:04.850
His whole life sheltering us

00:15:05.440 --> 00:15:07.300
To end this thousand-year feud, right?

00:15:07.440 --> 00:15:08.940
Yet look how he met his end.

00:15:12.870 --> 00:15:14.060
He fought for the immortal sects

00:15:15.080 --> 00:15:16.210
And strove tirelessly for all living beings.

00:15:17.680 --> 00:15:18.540
But what became of him?

00:15:20.560 --> 00:15:21.690
He died in unrest,

00:15:22.830 --> 00:15:23.940
And his soul scattered.

00:15:23.940 --> 00:15:26.690
♪Through the future snow, wind, and fog♪

00:15:26.870 --> 00:15:28.260
I can't bear to see you,

00:15:29.280 --> 00:15:30.330
Tongzhou,

00:15:31.350 --> 00:15:33.020
Gelin or the others die before me.

00:15:33.470 --> 00:15:34.690
Then why not join me?

00:15:35.710 --> 00:15:36.300
If we stand united,

00:15:36.320 --> 00:15:37.140
We can find a way together.

00:15:38.680 --> 00:15:39.690
There's no way left.

00:15:40.400 --> 00:15:41.090
The Sea Calamity looms near.

00:15:41.110 --> 00:15:41.940
Time is running out.

00:15:43.200 --> 00:15:44.210
You are the Demon Lord Yecha.

00:15:44.920 --> 00:15:46.180
You possess unmatched vitality

00:15:46.200 --> 00:15:47.450
To weather any calamity.

00:15:48.750 --> 00:15:49.570
But what about them?

00:15:51.800 --> 00:15:52.780
I won't let my friends get dragged

00:15:52.800 --> 00:15:53.940
Into trouble because of me.

00:15:54.510 --> 00:15:55.180
What do you mean?

00:15:56.750 --> 00:15:57.660
Are the immortal sects pressing you hard?

00:15:58.680 --> 00:16:02.560
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

00:16:02.560 --> 00:16:03.570
I'm not coming with you.

00:16:04.800 --> 00:16:05.730
That's all I'll say.

00:16:06.600 --> 00:16:08.800
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

00:16:08.800 --> 00:16:10.090
If you break into the barrier again...

00:16:10.400 --> 00:16:12.470
♪I wish you well♪

00:16:12.470 --> 00:16:14.570
We'll truly become enemies.

00:16:14.570 --> 00:16:15.520
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

00:16:15.880 --> 00:16:19.800
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

00:16:21.160 --> 00:16:22.800
♪You're still screaming♪

00:16:23.080 --> 00:16:27.400
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

00:16:27.840 --> 00:16:32.080
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

00:16:32.440 --> 00:16:33.630
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

00:16:33.630 --> 00:16:34.330
Lifei.

00:16:35.600 --> 00:16:37.760
♪I'd shatter my soul♪

00:16:40.040 --> 00:16:40.730
Don't go.

00:16:40.730 --> 00:16:42.680
♪To lay all your days in peace♪

00:16:43.280 --> 00:16:46.840
♪To wander with you♪

00:16:51.350 --> 00:16:51.970
Your Highness,

00:16:52.960 --> 00:16:53.730
Maybe

00:16:54.750 --> 00:16:55.540
Let it go.

00:17:03.200 --> 00:17:03.780
Lifei.

00:17:12.920 --> 00:17:13.900
I held you back

00:17:14.640 --> 00:17:15.140
Because...

00:17:15.160 --> 00:17:15.860
I know.

00:17:16.990 --> 00:17:17.940
The so-called cultivation partners

00:17:18.310 --> 00:17:19.180
Were only a temporary excuse.

00:17:19.920 --> 00:17:20.940
Don't let this weigh on you.

00:17:22.680 --> 00:17:24.450
You defended me in public.

00:17:25.160 --> 00:17:26.450
I can't let your words ring empty.

00:17:29.440 --> 00:17:30.730
As long as you stay safe,

00:17:31.270 --> 00:17:32.420
No matter how gravely I'm wounded,

00:17:32.710 --> 00:17:33.660
No matter how much slander I endure,

00:17:34.070 --> 00:17:34.970
I don't care at all.

00:17:35.360 --> 00:17:36.180
But I care deeply.

00:17:40.270 --> 00:17:41.420
You are my dearest friend.

00:17:42.600 --> 00:17:43.690
I won't let the immortal sects scorn

00:17:44.120 --> 00:17:46.100
And slander you because of me.

00:17:49.070 --> 00:17:50.620
I'm fickle by nature.

00:17:51.270 --> 00:17:52.380
We gather when joy fills our hearts,

00:17:52.840 --> 00:17:53.860
And part when the joy fades.

00:17:55.960 --> 00:17:58.010
So many bonds are destined to be fleeting.

00:17:59.160 --> 00:18:00.100
Will you blame me

00:18:02.200 --> 00:18:03.010
When that day comes?

00:18:06.960 --> 00:18:08.010
Whenever it is,

00:18:08.310 --> 00:18:09.180
And whatever choice you make,

00:18:09.880 --> 00:18:10.770
I shall never blame you.

00:18:11.550 --> 00:18:13.250
I'll only be glad for your choice.

00:18:16.310 --> 00:18:17.050
Tongzhou,

00:18:18.160 --> 00:18:19.450
I'm running out of time.

00:18:20.400 --> 00:18:21.340
If marrying you

00:18:21.680 --> 00:18:22.820
Can bring you happiness,

00:18:23.600 --> 00:18:24.730
I shall grant your wish.

00:18:26.990 --> 00:18:27.900
Could you give me

00:18:29.360 --> 00:18:30.490
That jade pendant again?

00:18:39.030 --> 00:18:39.660
What?

00:18:47.310 --> 00:18:48.420
Mr. Shen

00:18:48.550 --> 00:18:49.580
Has barely passed away,

00:18:49.920 --> 00:18:51.180
Not even a proper sacrifice for him.

00:18:51.440 --> 00:18:53.290
Yet some are rushing to hold

00:18:54.360 --> 00:18:55.490
A wedding feast.

00:18:57.230 --> 00:18:59.900
Ms. Shen has given her consent to His Highness

00:19:00.160 --> 00:19:02.010
And Lifei's wedding at the Wanxian Sect.

00:19:02.360 --> 00:19:04.660
Those petty, narrow-minded souls

00:19:04.960 --> 00:19:06.380
Only judge noble hearts

00:19:06.680 --> 00:19:07.690
By their own shallow minds.

00:19:16.320 --> 00:19:19.120
[Double Happiness]

00:19:23.120 --> 00:19:26.290
I only wish for you to live safe and sound.

00:19:27.440 --> 00:19:28.490
Rest assured, Master.

00:19:29.270 --> 00:19:30.180
I will be safe and sound.

00:19:34.840 --> 00:19:35.530
Lifei,

00:19:36.680 --> 00:19:37.940
Are you truly going to marry Tongzhou?

00:19:40.640 --> 00:19:41.380
What about Xiuyuan?

00:19:42.990 --> 00:19:43.940
Have you really let go of everything?

00:19:45.440 --> 00:19:46.530
The Sea Calamity draws near.

00:19:47.230 --> 00:19:48.580
We have our own mission to fulfill.

00:19:49.790 --> 00:19:51.340
I just can't figure you out.

00:19:53.510 --> 00:19:54.340
Forget it.

00:19:55.160 --> 00:19:56.690
Such is the cruel twist of fate.

00:19:58.550 --> 00:19:59.580
No matter what choice you make,

00:19:59.880 --> 00:20:00.770
I'll stand by you.

00:20:03.790 --> 00:20:04.660
Didn't you bring a wedding gift?

00:20:05.120 --> 00:20:06.340
Tomorrow is no ordinary day.

00:20:06.600 --> 00:20:07.340
Came empty-handed?

00:20:08.470 --> 00:20:09.580
Don't you trust me?

00:20:15.710 --> 00:20:17.530
I had no idea what gift to get you.

00:20:18.510 --> 00:20:19.580
There's an old saying from my hometown

00:20:20.270 --> 00:20:21.770
That those who wear paired heart-knots

00:20:21.790 --> 00:20:23.770
Shall stand as one, bringing safety and luck.

00:20:25.230 --> 00:20:27.210
I visited the temple to get two

00:20:27.230 --> 00:20:27.900
As a gift for you both.

00:20:57.990 --> 00:20:58.690
Miaoqing?

00:21:05.840 --> 00:21:08.340
Unsure what bridal dowry you'll need,

00:21:08.790 --> 00:21:10.450
I had Miaoqing prepare more.

00:21:10.920 --> 00:21:11.820
Check if these please you.

00:21:15.440 --> 00:21:16.490
When I first saw you,

00:21:17.510 --> 00:21:19.530
Your maid spilled golden powder on the street,

00:21:20.230 --> 00:21:21.580
And you sat in a golden carriage.

00:21:22.270 --> 00:21:23.620
The whole sight made you look

00:21:23.640 --> 00:21:25.490
Like a plump sheep cast entirely of gold.

00:21:26.920 --> 00:21:27.730
Right then, I made up my mind

00:21:28.400 --> 00:21:29.180
To cling

00:21:29.510 --> 00:21:30.770
To this wealthy patron for good.

00:21:32.920 --> 00:21:34.010
So you got close to me

00:21:34.790 --> 00:21:35.860
Just because of my wealth?

00:21:37.790 --> 00:21:38.730
Not at all.

00:21:38.990 --> 00:21:39.820
You're nice.

00:21:40.470 --> 00:21:41.860
I traveled with my master far and wide,

00:21:42.360 --> 00:21:43.340
So I'm good at judging people.

00:21:44.200 --> 00:21:45.420
High-ranking you may be,

00:21:46.400 --> 00:21:47.490
Yet you're good-hearted,

00:21:47.990 --> 00:21:49.690
Righteous, and generous.

00:21:53.030 --> 00:21:53.580
Tongzhou,

00:21:54.920 --> 00:21:57.530
The bond we once shared will never fade.

00:22:05.360 --> 00:22:05.820
By the way,

00:22:08.640 --> 00:22:09.380
Take a look at this.

00:22:11.400 --> 00:22:12.180
What is it?

00:22:13.200 --> 00:22:14.940
Rouge refined from Yunmeng Blossoms of the East Sea,

00:22:15.440 --> 00:22:16.180
Extremely rare to come by.

00:22:39.230 --> 00:22:40.660
Battered by successive injuries,

00:22:41.310 --> 00:22:42.380
Your spirit power is greatly depleted.

00:22:43.270 --> 00:22:44.180
At this rate,

00:22:44.640 --> 00:22:46.490
You can barely suppress the curse.

00:22:47.990 --> 00:22:48.690
By the way, sir,

00:22:50.360 --> 00:22:51.660
You've lived with Master for many years.

00:22:52.400 --> 00:22:55.530
Have you heard of or seen the Xuantian Biluo Compass?

00:22:56.640 --> 00:22:58.620
The Xuantian Biluo Compass?

00:23:00.360 --> 00:23:01.770
Master once mentioned

00:23:02.200 --> 00:23:03.970
He used an ancient compass

00:23:04.230 --> 00:23:05.490
To travel back to the Central Plains.

00:23:06.200 --> 00:23:06.900
After his return,

00:23:07.070 --> 00:23:08.660
He hid it on Hushe Peak.

00:23:09.230 --> 00:23:11.140
Later, he was labeled as a sect traitor

00:23:11.440 --> 00:23:12.690
And was hunted down by Cuixuan,

00:23:13.310 --> 00:23:14.340
So he fled in such a desperate hurry

00:23:14.680 --> 00:23:15.450
And had no chance to take it with him.

00:23:16.120 --> 00:23:16.820
I believe it must be

00:23:17.270 --> 00:23:19.860
The Xuantian Biluo Compass you mentioned.

00:23:20.880 --> 00:23:21.820
Most likely so.

00:23:24.440 --> 00:23:27.140
So when Master fetched the compass on Hushe Peak,

00:23:28.440 --> 00:23:30.940
He was ambushed by Cuixuan.

00:23:34.750 --> 00:23:36.940
Master Qingcheng always wished

00:23:36.960 --> 00:23:38.900
For you and Lifei to live safely.

00:23:40.070 --> 00:23:41.660
When he learned of your true identity,

00:23:42.030 --> 00:23:43.420
He feared you couldn't enter the Central Plains,

00:23:43.880 --> 00:23:45.420
So he resolved to risk his life and return.

00:23:46.160 --> 00:23:47.250
Then this compass

00:23:47.270 --> 00:23:49.140
Must be in Cuixuan's hand.

00:23:51.710 --> 00:23:52.770
We must find it.

00:23:54.270 --> 00:23:55.340
Only with the compass

00:23:56.360 --> 00:23:58.140
Can we locate the passage during the Sea Calamity

00:23:59.440 --> 00:24:00.940
And send our clansmen back to the islands.

00:24:04.120 --> 00:24:04.770
My Lord.

00:24:06.550 --> 00:24:06.970
My Lord.

00:24:09.840 --> 00:24:10.970
News comes from Duanming City.

00:24:11.470 --> 00:24:13.180
Ji Tongzhou will marry Jiang Lifei.

00:24:13.710 --> 00:24:14.210
What?

00:24:30.990 --> 00:24:31.770
Qingcheng.

00:24:33.030 --> 00:24:33.730
Riyan.

00:24:36.960 --> 00:24:39.050
I learned that this Nine-Tailed Fox is a born spirit beast

00:24:39.790 --> 00:24:41.100
With cultivation of at least a thousand years.

00:24:42.310 --> 00:24:44.730
Never expected such intimate terms between them.

00:24:46.030 --> 00:24:48.490
Demons and monsters are adept at corrupting humans.

00:24:49.680 --> 00:24:51.340
Bewitched by Riyan,

00:24:52.070 --> 00:24:53.420
Qingcheng disregarded all mortal lives,

00:24:53.680 --> 00:24:54.770
Betrayed his sect,

00:24:55.550 --> 00:24:57.620
And cared only for those alien beasts.

00:24:58.710 --> 00:24:59.580
Lifei is different from the rest.

00:25:00.750 --> 00:25:01.530
You promised

00:25:01.960 --> 00:25:02.690
You wouldn't harm her.

00:25:03.070 --> 00:25:04.490
I can give up the Divine Tree.

00:25:05.160 --> 00:25:05.730
But

00:25:06.270 --> 00:25:07.660
Will Lei Xiuyuan come?

00:25:08.550 --> 00:25:09.250
He will.

00:25:30.640 --> 00:25:32.860
Taiji produces two modes;

00:25:33.510 --> 00:25:35.450
Yin and Yang spring from one source;

00:25:36.550 --> 00:25:38.490
Heaven and Earth unite in the Great Dao;

00:25:39.120 --> 00:25:41.210
The path of eternal life lies ahead.

00:25:58.360 --> 00:25:59.340
On this blessed, auspicious day,

00:25:59.750 --> 00:26:00.860
A noble lord meets his fair maiden.

00:26:01.510 --> 00:26:03.660
Here stands Prince Ji Tongzhou of Yue,

00:26:04.120 --> 00:26:05.820
And Jiang Lifei of Qingqiu.

00:26:06.510 --> 00:26:07.660
Your love is a golden-jade fate,

00:26:07.790 --> 00:26:08.820
And your marriage forged by heaven's will.

00:26:09.600 --> 00:26:11.420
May you live in marital harmony,

00:26:11.840 --> 00:26:12.900
Support each other always,

00:26:13.440 --> 00:26:14.820
Uphold the great Dao of heaven and earth,

00:26:15.200 --> 00:26:16.770
Seal your eternal bond of one heart,

00:26:16.840 --> 00:26:18.580
And journey together down the immortal path.

00:26:26.440 --> 00:26:27.210
The auspicious hour arrives.

00:26:27.840 --> 00:26:29.010
The newlyweds shall bind their heart seal.

00:27:00.510 --> 00:27:01.290
Jiang Lifei!

00:27:10.710 --> 00:27:11.250
Demon Lord!

00:27:28.440 --> 00:27:29.340
- After him. - He's running away!

00:27:29.360 --> 00:27:30.010
Seize him!

00:27:38.790 --> 00:27:39.210
Never mind.

00:27:39.990 --> 00:27:40.660
Let the ceremony go on.

00:27:58.790 --> 00:27:59.380
Jiang Lifei!

00:28:19.960 --> 00:28:20.490
Lifei,

00:28:21.070 --> 00:28:21.730
Don't marry him!

00:28:37.310 --> 00:28:38.340
You've finally come.

00:28:41.600 --> 00:28:42.490
What are you waiting for?

00:29:16.710 --> 00:29:17.290
Cuixuan,

00:29:18.360 --> 00:29:19.180
I knew you would show yourself.

00:29:22.200 --> 00:29:22.770
Miaoqing,

00:29:23.160 --> 00:29:23.900
Go back first.

00:29:47.160 --> 00:29:47.690
Are you alright?

00:29:49.230 --> 00:29:49.860
I'm fine.

00:29:55.840 --> 00:29:56.770
You're Lifei?

00:30:03.750 --> 00:30:04.340
Did you think

00:30:05.270 --> 00:30:06.010
I was Miaoqing?

00:30:53.230 --> 00:30:54.180
That rouge refined from Yunmeng Blossoms

00:30:54.200 --> 00:30:55.010
Can knock people unconscious.

00:30:56.470 --> 00:30:57.620
Roaming the martial world for years,

00:30:58.030 --> 00:30:58.730
I certainly know that.

00:31:01.070 --> 00:31:02.620
So you played along with my trick

00:31:03.400 --> 00:31:04.940
And pretended to be Miaoqing to test me.

00:31:05.470 --> 00:31:07.100
I needed to find out what you planned.

00:31:07.640 --> 00:31:08.490
I even guessed

00:31:09.310 --> 00:31:10.620
You'd use me to capture Lei Xiuyuan.

00:31:14.120 --> 00:31:15.140
But I never imagined

00:31:17.600 --> 00:31:19.050
You would collude with Cuixuan.

00:31:23.600 --> 00:31:24.580
Haven't you figured it out yet?

00:31:25.920 --> 00:31:29.420
His Highness and I have long joined forces.

00:31:30.470 --> 00:31:33.140
This whole trap today is to slay the Demon Lord

00:31:33.640 --> 00:31:35.180
And save the Central Plains from catastrophe.

00:31:35.550 --> 00:31:37.380
This is for the greater good.

00:31:38.310 --> 00:31:39.660
Causing the monster chaos

00:31:40.070 --> 00:31:41.100
And killing Mr. Shen

00:31:41.640 --> 00:31:42.660
Are for the greater good, too?

00:31:47.400 --> 00:31:49.050
You cowardly villain!

00:31:50.270 --> 00:31:52.290
I'll make you pay with your life for my master and Mr. Shen.

00:32:24.270 --> 00:32:25.380
You can wield the Senluo Grand Art, too?

00:32:26.400 --> 00:32:27.050
Girl,

00:32:28.440 --> 00:32:29.730
Your cultivation is far too shallow.

00:32:30.160 --> 00:32:32.140
Your Senluo Grand Art

00:32:32.840 --> 00:32:35.250
Is not even one thousandth as powerful as Qingcheng's.

00:32:37.160 --> 00:32:38.620
You despicable lowlife!

00:32:39.160 --> 00:32:40.210
Don't you compare yourself to my master.

00:32:41.360 --> 00:32:42.010
Silence!

00:32:50.360 --> 00:32:50.860
Lifei!

00:32:53.200 --> 00:32:53.770
Lifei!

00:33:00.790 --> 00:33:02.050
We're in the Senluo Grand Art.

00:33:02.400 --> 00:33:03.050
Exactly.

00:33:03.550 --> 00:33:05.620
Now that you've stepped into my Senluo territory,

00:33:06.120 --> 00:33:07.450
None of you shall leave alive.

00:33:07.990 --> 00:33:08.970
Where did you hide

00:33:09.640 --> 00:33:10.250
Qingcheng's belongings?

00:33:10.960 --> 00:33:12.530
That worthless foreign trash

00:33:13.070 --> 00:33:13.940
Serves no purpose in keeping it.

00:33:14.360 --> 00:33:15.340
I destroyed it long ago.

00:33:52.440 --> 00:33:53.100
Are you alright?

00:33:57.440 --> 00:33:58.100
Cuixuan,

00:33:58.750 --> 00:33:59.970
You offered yourself as a sacrifice to demons!

00:34:00.470 --> 00:34:01.730
There was no other way

00:34:02.360 --> 00:34:05.770
To defeat the scheming Demon Lord.

00:34:06.750 --> 00:34:08.490
Any power boost,

00:34:08.960 --> 00:34:10.100
Be it demonic energy

00:34:10.600 --> 00:34:11.180
Or spirit energy,

00:34:11.710 --> 00:34:13.130
I will take all of it.

00:34:16.470 --> 00:34:17.900
Even your Yecha power

00:34:19.670 --> 00:34:20.940
Shall be mine to seize.

00:34:21.510 --> 00:34:22.340
So you capture me

00:34:23.070 --> 00:34:24.610
Just to absorb my Yecha power.

00:34:25.470 --> 00:34:25.940
But

00:34:26.510 --> 00:34:27.650
Why did you kill Mr. Shen?

00:34:28.510 --> 00:34:31.820
Like Qingcheng, he was blind to right and wrong,

00:34:31.840 --> 00:34:32.860
Stubborn beyond reason.

00:34:33.190 --> 00:34:36.610
He allied with the demon clan to stand against the Sea Calamity.

00:34:37.070 --> 00:34:38.860
No inhuman fiend can ever be trusted.

00:34:41.400 --> 00:34:42.260
Meet your end!

00:35:24.280 --> 00:35:25.050
What is this?

00:35:25.960 --> 00:35:27.530
Master Qingcheng's spirit-controlling spell.

00:35:28.280 --> 00:35:29.740
You've absorbed my clan's demonic energy.

00:35:30.190 --> 00:35:30.780
Now,

00:35:31.400 --> 00:35:32.260
Offer your flesh and blood

00:35:32.470 --> 00:35:33.260
To sacrifice them.

00:36:16.240 --> 00:36:16.700
Master!

00:36:37.550 --> 00:36:38.130
Master!

00:36:38.760 --> 00:36:39.380
Master!

00:36:39.990 --> 00:36:40.820
Master,

00:36:42.590 --> 00:36:44.050
I've avenged you at last.

00:36:47.590 --> 00:36:48.300
Master!

00:36:54.360 --> 00:36:55.700
The Xuantian Biluo Compass.

00:37:01.280 --> 00:37:01.820
Xiuyuan.

00:37:06.110 --> 00:37:06.650
Enough!

00:37:14.030 --> 00:37:15.220
This farce shall end here.

00:37:19.550 --> 00:37:20.050
Run!

00:37:45.110 --> 00:37:45.970
You've been struck by the Burning Flame Force.

00:37:53.360 --> 00:37:54.380
No cure exists for this.

00:37:55.630 --> 00:37:56.700
It's too late.

00:37:59.400 --> 00:38:01.300
Jiaping, don't give up!

00:38:01.320 --> 00:38:02.050
Ji Tongzhou.

00:38:03.440 --> 00:38:03.970
Xiuyuan,

00:38:05.150 --> 00:38:06.050
Leave with Jiaping first.

00:38:06.800 --> 00:38:07.490
I'll hold Tongzhou back.

00:38:08.400 --> 00:38:09.340
Find a way to dispel the poison.

00:38:10.510 --> 00:38:11.610
I have my own duty to fulfill,

00:38:12.150 --> 00:38:13.130
And you do what you must.

00:38:13.880 --> 00:38:14.420
Lifei.

00:38:14.590 --> 00:38:15.220
Go!

00:38:21.280 --> 00:38:21.700
Go!

00:39:07.110 --> 00:39:07.940
Where is Lei Xiuyuan?

00:39:09.030 --> 00:39:09.740
He's gone.

00:39:11.360 --> 00:39:12.260
You let him escape.

00:39:13.400 --> 00:39:14.740
So you side with the demon clan

00:39:15.240 --> 00:39:16.490
And stand against all the immortal sects?

00:39:17.400 --> 00:39:18.570
I take no side.

00:39:19.630 --> 00:39:21.450
I was born from heaven and earth as a fruit,

00:39:22.070 --> 00:39:22.820
Bound to no faction.

00:39:23.440 --> 00:39:24.130
Immortals

00:39:25.070 --> 00:39:25.650
Or demons alike.

00:39:27.240 --> 00:39:28.490
I only abide by the justice in my heart.

00:39:29.550 --> 00:39:30.740
My only wish now

00:39:31.400 --> 00:39:32.530
Is that everyone shall survive

00:39:33.800 --> 00:39:34.940
The Sea Calamity.

00:39:37.550 --> 00:39:38.340
Everyone?

00:39:39.720 --> 00:39:41.570
You're worried about Lei Xiuyuan, right?

00:39:42.440 --> 00:39:45.170
He is the only one you have ever cared for.

00:39:46.720 --> 00:39:48.740
You never truly wanted to marry me.

00:39:51.070 --> 00:39:52.090
I agreed to the marriage

00:39:54.720 --> 00:39:56.260
Only hoping that before I face death,

00:39:57.470 --> 00:39:59.530
All of us could let go of hatred

00:40:00.150 --> 00:40:01.050
And carry fewer regrets.

00:40:02.240 --> 00:40:03.860
Yet as the calamity looms near,

00:40:04.800 --> 00:40:06.650
You've conspired with Cuixuan to deceive me.

00:40:06.670 --> 00:40:07.860
Has he never lied to you?

00:40:13.920 --> 00:40:16.900
He schemed against you and hurt you back then.

00:40:17.880 --> 00:40:19.010
You can forgive

00:40:19.440 --> 00:40:20.490
All his plots and tricks,

00:40:21.590 --> 00:40:23.010
But what of my risking my life for you?

00:40:26.070 --> 00:40:27.340
As soon as he appears,

00:40:28.400 --> 00:40:30.300
You leave with him without hesitation.

00:40:33.240 --> 00:40:34.220
I forgive him,

00:40:35.960 --> 00:40:37.260
And I shall forgive you just the same.

00:40:41.670 --> 00:40:43.260
Ever since we met in our youth,

00:40:44.360 --> 00:40:46.450
We've endured countless hardships.

00:40:48.510 --> 00:40:50.170
Xiuyuan is the love of my life.

00:40:51.840 --> 00:40:52.780
Yet the life-or-death bond

00:40:54.280 --> 00:40:55.700
Among the three of us

00:40:55.720 --> 00:40:56.610
Is more precious than anything.

00:40:56.960 --> 00:40:58.650
Those old vows to share weal and woe

00:40:58.670 --> 00:40:59.650
Were never empty.

00:41:00.150 --> 00:41:01.050
Whether fighting against Zong Quan,

00:41:02.720 --> 00:41:03.650
On Fanghu Island,

00:41:04.760 --> 00:41:05.650
Or in Duantu,

00:41:06.190 --> 00:41:07.490
We entrusted our lives to one another.

00:41:08.800 --> 00:41:10.610
Why must it all come to this?

00:41:12.400 --> 00:41:14.300
He is the root of all disasters.

00:41:17.190 --> 00:41:18.170
Not he,

00:41:20.920 --> 00:41:23.010
But human selfishness and greed.

00:41:26.990 --> 00:41:27.650
Tongzhou,

00:41:28.320 --> 00:41:29.530
The Sea Calamity is upon us.

00:41:29.840 --> 00:41:31.450
Far more critical tasks await us.

00:41:32.510 --> 00:41:33.220
Let this grudge rest.

00:41:35.030 --> 00:41:35.940
Speak of it no more.

00:41:45.240 --> 00:41:46.130
What else do you want to do?

00:41:47.190 --> 00:41:48.130
None of you shall leave.

00:42:03.030 --> 00:42:03.530
Mr. Hu.

00:42:14.550 --> 00:42:15.780
I told you to lead them away.

00:42:16.880 --> 00:42:17.820
Why did you return?

00:42:22.440 --> 00:42:23.820
As Lifei's senior brother

00:42:25.760 --> 00:42:26.970
And your guardian,

00:42:29.110 --> 00:42:33.050
I should shield you from harm.

00:42:37.880 --> 00:42:38.860
Have you found the compass?

00:42:42.050 --> 00:42:42.360
[The Eternal Fragrance]

00:42:42.360 --> 00:42:44.560
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

00:42:57.500 --> 00:43:01.020
♪The warmth within my arms♪

00:43:01.180 --> 00:43:04.700
♪I can no longer hold on to♪

00:43:04.820 --> 00:43:08.340
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

00:43:08.460 --> 00:43:11.940
♪Keep you warm until sunrise?♪

00:43:11.940 --> 00:43:15.580
♪My heartbeat freezes♪

00:43:15.980 --> 00:43:19.260
♪I can no longer tell you♪

00:43:19.380 --> 00:43:22.900
♪Looking you in the eyes, I cannot♪

00:43:22.940 --> 00:43:25.940
♪Utter that line♪

00:43:26.100 --> 00:43:28.140
♪Knowing love and hate♪

00:43:28.220 --> 00:43:32.620
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

00:43:33.340 --> 00:43:35.420
♪I still linger on♪

00:43:35.580 --> 00:43:39.860
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

00:43:40.020 --> 00:43:44.540
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

00:43:44.620 --> 00:43:48.140
♪But we thought nothing of it♪

00:43:48.220 --> 00:43:51.660
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

00:43:51.940 --> 00:43:55.180
♪I wish you well♪

00:43:55.340 --> 00:43:57.060
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

00:43:57.220 --> 00:44:01.900
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

00:44:02.500 --> 00:44:04.580
♪You're still screaming♪

00:44:04.740 --> 00:44:09.220
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

00:44:09.340 --> 00:44:13.820
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

00:44:14.060 --> 00:44:17.020
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

00:44:17.140 --> 00:44:19.020
♪Leaping straight into♪

00:44:19.140 --> 00:44:23.900
♪That heartbreaking past♪

00:44:24.140 --> 00:44:27.660
♪Just to keep you safe♪

00:44:34.100 --> 00:44:37.420
♪My breath is about to stop♪

00:44:37.540 --> 00:44:41.060
♪Those hands can no longer hold yours♪

00:44:41.180 --> 00:44:44.620
♪Through the future snow, wind, and fog♪

00:44:44.780 --> 00:44:47.980
♪Who will be there by your side?♪

00:44:48.100 --> 00:44:51.820
♪I smile as it ends♪

00:44:51.980 --> 00:44:55.620
♪Afraid that you might cry for me♪

00:44:55.820 --> 00:44:59.220
♪Quietly, I turn into a sky lantern♪

00:44:59.380 --> 00:45:02.500
♪To light your way through the night♪

00:45:02.580 --> 00:45:04.620
♪Knowing love and hate♪

00:45:04.700 --> 00:45:09.100
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

00:45:09.860 --> 00:45:11.900
♪I still linger on♪

00:45:12.060 --> 00:45:16.340
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

00:45:16.500 --> 00:45:21.020
♪The storm looms, yet I stand in its way♪

00:45:21.100 --> 00:45:24.300
♪Torn inside, still I burn bright♪

00:45:24.500 --> 00:45:26.460
♪With the light from my fingertips♪

00:45:26.540 --> 00:45:30.940
♪I build a paradise♪

00:45:31.100 --> 00:45:34.580
♪To wander with you♪

